{
  "stem": "1419.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of them-- most of them came from Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think from Israel we came maybe 30, 30 people in a bus load.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one came from Miami, which is from Nowy Targ.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one is living in, in London.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came from London.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we get-- we got up in the morning and walked to the school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't live in the school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived in three houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- they were put with barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The guard-- the guards were all Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were marched every day to school-- to the school to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A lot of people worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of them worked in the-- feeding the cows or the pigs and cleaning the-- cleaning the streets, whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I worked on building the, the target range.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we built it for, for maybe six months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So what was the, the whole-- the whole job was to, to work with a pic and to pick it up with shovels, put it on a-- on a wheelbarrow and take away the mud and haul it away and build a [? big-- ?] a [? big ?] target range, which was-- I don't know how many yards.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It must have been about maybe 200 or 300 yards long, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we built the road coming to the-- to the-- to the target range and inside the target range.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we built bunkers, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When they-- when they-- when they built the target range, they set up targets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There had to be a bunker, big, big bunkers that the people could move, move around in the back and set up the targets.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's how I worked over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Water coming down.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
